rows.label: qst101501_msg0003
rows.name: Boats sold not paid for yet...

rows.label: qst101501_msg0004
rows.name: Just-built boats get all smashed up...

rows.label: qst101501_msg0005
rows.name:
And if that not enough, someone
ransack Umon's Shipyard too...

rows.label: qst101501_msg0006
rows.name:
Umon no longer have will to live.
All Umon good for now is reabsorb
life force back into Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0007
rows.name:
Umon not care who wreck his ships
anymore...

rows.label: qst101501_msg0009
rows.name:
Mehmeh? You help me jump into
Cloud Sea?

rows.label: qst101501_msg0010
rows.name:
Maybe if Umon had new boat to fix up,
would not be at end of own rope.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0011
rows.name:
But hopes of that are deader than fried
fish.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0012
rows.name:
Umon not have Green Pollen Orb
anymore.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0013
rows.name: That mean no new Divine Beasts will come.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0014
rows.name:
Mehmeh! Tora and friends look
for new Divine Beast for Umon?

rows.label: qst101501_msg0015
rows.name:
Okay. Then Umon not jump into
Cloud Sea just yet.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0016
rows.name:
Should probably make body heavier to
hasten demise anyway.

rows.label: qst101501_msg0017
rows.name:
Umon go and force down many tasty
treats in canteen at Grodd Residential
Zone.
